\section{Changes in version 1.7.0 (2014-01-29)}{
  \itemize{
    \item{Applied Biosystems' binary converter replaced by seqinr package's read.abif(), enabling compatibility with most operating systems.}
    \item{Dependency to XML package dropped, dependency to tcltk made optional.}
    \item{Windows file selection dialogues replaced by Tcl-tk ones.}
    \item{Examples added to most of the help pages.}
    \item{offScale attribute in 'fsa' objects simplified as vectors (channel data seems spurious).}
    \item{outThreshold argument in align.fsa() can now be defined as a proportion (new default value).}
    \item{MLPA.interface() no longer proposes a default design path (second occurence removed).}
    \item{modelizeNoise() deleted, as deprecated.}
  }
}
\section{Changes in version 1.6.0 (2014-01-24)}{
